# Package Manager Rules
always use pnpm
never use npm
never use yarn
never use npx
replace npx with pnpm dlx
suggest pnpm add instead of npm install
suggest pnpm install instead of npm install
suggest pnpm create instead of npm create

# Workspace Rules
use pnpm workspaces
suggest -w flag for workspace-wide installations
suggest --filter for package-specific commands
suggest pnpm add -w for workspace root dependencies
suggest pnpm add --filter <package> for package-specific dependencies

# Framework Rules
when using expo suggest solutions using version 52 or newer
